e row.\", \"from\": 2068, \"to\": 2132, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After India's underwhelming start on Day 1 in Paris Olympics 2024 as shooters were eliminated in the 10m air rifle mixed team qualification stage as well as 10m air pistol men's qualification, Manu Bhaker was at the top of her game as she entered the 10m women's air pistol final.\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2414, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2140, \"end\": 2145, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.545123776229505e-19, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}, {\"begin\": 2327, \"end\": 2338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manu_Bhaker\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Manu Bhaker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manu_Bhaker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manu_Bhaker\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Rowing, India's lone rower Balraj Panwar moved to the repechages after finishing fourth.\", \"from\": 2416, \"to\": 2507, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, Chinese divers Chang Yani and Chen Yiwen bagged the first Olympic gold.\", \"from\": 2508, \"to\": 2590, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2519, \"end\": 2526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9993532236679624, \"rank\": 0.0005527447691901621, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 2534, \"end\": 2544, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chang_Yani\", \"score\": 0.999957464354512, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chang Yani\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chang_Yani\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chang_Yani\"}, {\"begin\": 2549, \"end\": 2559, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.